data.description: Beautiful move-in ready low maintenance ALL BRICK Townhouse in the heart of Knox County in the highly sought subdivision of Wisteria Plantation.  This 3 bedroom 2.5 bath home features a spacious living area complete with master on the main, ensuite with double sinks, a walk-in tile shower, and a spacious walk-in closet. The kitchen comes with an island/breakfast bar, pantry, stainless steel appliances and lots of cabinet space.  New water heater AND this beauty is already equipped with a water filtration system featuring reverse osmosis. The laundry room is on the main as well.  The 2nd floor features 2 additional bedrooms, a bonus room, full bath and a partially finished spacious room that could easily become an additional bedroom, flex or additional storage room. Enjoy your private patio area outside with peaceful views. Amazing location just minutes from downtown Knoxville, Sevierville, hospitals, restaurants, shopping, parks and so much more!!! This gem won't last long.  Schedule your private showing today!
